    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873240/extras/f1a4cbf262f656729771443276cc9997.avif?t=1765259872\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873240/extras_big/f1a4cbf262f656729771443276cc9997.avif?t=1765259872 width=800 height=266 /></span></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💣 Bomberrage – 爆炸性的多人对战！</strong></p>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>概述：</strong> 进入<strong>Bomberrage</strong>的混乱世界，这是一款快节奏、充满动作的多人游戏，策略与反应决定谁能生存！与智能AI对战，或挑战朋友，在每一秒都至关重要的爆炸性战斗中一决高下！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点：</strong></h2>  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>紧张刺激的多人战斗</strong> – 在动态炸弹对战中，与AI或真实玩家一较高下！  <br>🧠 <strong>高难度AI对手</strong> – 适应并智胜无情的敌人！  <br>🗺 <strong>不断变化的竞技场</strong> – 通过程序生成地图，让每场战斗都充满新鲜感！  <br>🎮 <strong>易上手，难精通</strong> – 休闲玩家可以轻松享受，竞技玩家也能获得挑战！  <br>🎬 <strong>史诗级动画&amp;独特角色</strong> – 爆炸场面从未如此震撼！</p>",
